DNSdumpster.com is a domain research tool that can be used by attackers to discover hosts related to a domain

-> Website:- https://dnsdumpster.com/

-> DNSDumpster.com is a FREE domain research tool that can discover hosts related to a domain. 

-> Finding visible hosts from the attackers perspective is an important part of the security assessment process.

-> In DnsDumspter as you will go to the website at home page you will be able to see search button just type over there your target website 

-> User will get the subdomains, IP address of the subdomains of the target website

-> User can get the information about the location at which country does subdomains of target website has been deployed

-> Also user get information that at what server does the subdomains is been using
